{
  "texts": [
    "Consumers have some responsibility for the environmental problems caused by landfilling or incinerating discarded clothing.",
    "As a consumer, you should take some responsibility for reducing clothing pollution.",
    "Personal Norms (PN) PN1 I feel I must contribute to reducing the problem of clothing pollution.",
    "Li and Shao (2023)",
    "We must all consider the environmental impact of clothing when we buy it."
  ]
}